output.name: GlassLensWatch
output.description: GlassLensWatch is an independent, nonprofit newsroom dedicated to investigative journalism in the public interest. With a team of over 100 journalists, it specializes in data-driven, accountability reporting that uncovers wrongdoing across government and society to spur real-world change. Committed to diversity, equity and inclusion, GlassLensWatch offers comprehensive benefits and an environment that empowers journalists to produce deep investigative work and drive impact.
